ort corridor, construction sites across the city. A car is not a luxury in Applewood. It is the difference between getting to work on time and missing shifts.\n\nMany Applewood residents spend $300-800 per month on taxis, ride shares, and borrowing rides from coworkers. A financed vehicle with NewWheels often costs less per month than these alternatives — and you own the vehicle at the end.\n\n## How to get started\n\n1. Fill out the free application on this page — takes under 3 minutes\n2. A NewWheels specialist reviews your file and matches you with the best lender\n3. Get approved within 24 hours — most same-day\n4. Choose your vehicle from dealerships across Calgary\n5. Drive home to Applewood with 6 months of payments covered",
